### вњ… Real Spring Boot Service вЂ” Full Example

```java
// Student.java (Entity)
@Data
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
@Builder
@Entity
public class Student {

    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;

    private String name;
    private int age;
    private String email;
}
```

```java
// StudentService.java
@Slf4j
@Service
@RequiredArgsConstructor   // constructor injection вЂ” no @Autowired needed
public class StudentService {

    private final StudentRepository studentRepo;  // auto-injected

    public Student createStudent(String name, int age) {
        log.info("Creating student: {}", name);

        Student s = Student.builder()
            .name(name)
            .age(age)
            .build();

        return studentRepo.save(s);
    }
}
```

```java
// StudentController.java
@Slf4j
@RestController
@RequiredArgsConstructor
@RequestMapping("/students")
public class StudentController {

    private final StudentService studentService;  // auto-injected

    @PostMapping
    public Student create(@RequestBody Student student) {
        log.info("POST /students called");
        return studentService.createStudent(
            student.getName(),
            student.getAge()
        );
    }
}
```

